20/05/2010
ATHENS, Greece -- The terror organisation Conspiracy Nuclei of Fire on Wednesday (May 19th) claimed responsibility for two bombings last week.
The blasts, one near a prison in Athens and the other near the court in Thessaloniki, left two people injured.
The claim of responsibility -- made in an internet statement -- is being investigated for authenticity.
(Reuters, AP - 19/05/10)
